metadata.description:
When balancing day-to-day life & what comes with reaching for your best self, roadblocks begin to reveal themselves as inevitable forces that have to be worked 'with' as opposed to worked 'against'. The energy surrounded around the shouldering of those burdens becomes ever-present throughout the 8-minute 42-second roller coaster presented by GREGNWMN. 

Inducing what best can be described as an ‘active’ listen, ‘FORCE' featuring JAHMED and ICECOLDBISHOP calls out to the most frustrating emotions that can rise to the surface at a moments notice, presenting how a hotheaded approach to life’s latent challenges are innately necessary emotions, capturing human nature in its most primal form. 

The Golden Egg Collector will receive an alternatively mixed offline bounce of GREGNWMNs debut EP 'BREAK THE CLOUDS' in full alongside early access to the upcoming merchandise collection associated with the release. 

34.5362° N 117.2928° W
BEST RECEIVED AT HIGH VOLUME
RUN TIME: 8 MINUTES + 42 SECONDS 
PRODUCED BY: D. SANDERS
MIXED + MASTERED BY: EDWIN GONZALEZ
